\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ z_{n}\right\} _{n=0}^{\infty}$
\end_inset

，若复数 
\begin_inset Formula $z_{*}$
\end_inset

 满足
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\forall\varepsilon>0\text{，存在无穷多个 }n\text{ 使得 }d(z_{*},z_{n})<\varepsilon
\]

\end_inset

